'''巾帼百名'''（{{lang-en|''100 Women''}}）是[[英国广播公司|BBC]]于2013年设立的系列节目，该节目研究21世纪女性角色，曾在伦敦<ref name=BBCNews-100Women-WhoIsTakingPart-2013>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-24579511|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|title=100 Women: Who is taking part?|date=2013-10-22|accessdate=2020-11-24|archive-date=2013-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107203737/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-24579511|dead-url=no}}</ref>和墨西哥举办过活动<ref name=BBCNews-100Women-Mexico-2016>{{cite news|last1=Low|first1=Harry|title=100 Women 2016: Mexico festival draws thousands|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38101195|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|date=2016-11-25|accessdate=2020-11-24|archive-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213020729/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38101195|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.inmujeres.cdmx.gob.mx/participa-inmujerescdmx-en-festival-100-women-de-la-bbc/|title=Participa Inmujeres CDMX en el festival 100 Women de la BBC|date=2016-11-24|work=CDMX|language=es|access-date=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220091507/http://www.inmujeres.cdmx.gob.mx/participa-inmujerescdmx-en-festival-100-women-de-la-bbc/|archive-date=2016-12-20|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。榜单揭晓后也是“BBC女性季”的开始，持续三周，包括开展广播、网络报道、辩论和关于女性话题的新闻报道等<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bengaluru/Saalumarada-Thimmakka-in-BBCs-100-Women-list/articleshow/55573030.cms|title=Saalumarada Thimmakka in BBC's 100 Women list|date=2016-11-23|work=[[印度时报|The Times of India]]|accessdate=2019-01-03|archive-date=2016-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127035525/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bengaluru/Saalumarada-Thimmakka-in-BBCs-100-Women-list/articleshow/55573030.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。节目鼓励世界各地的女性通过[[Twitter|Twitter]]参与，对榜单以及榜单发布后的采访和辩论发表评论<ref name=LebanonStar-2014>{{cite news|last=Stoughton|first=India|title=Lebanon makes its mark on BBC’s 100 Women list|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2014/Oct-28/275679-lebanon-makes-its-mark-on-bbcs-100-women-list.ashx|accessdate=2016-12-06|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Star_(Lebanon)|The Daily Star]]|date=2014-10-28|location=Beirut, Lebanon|archive-date=2016-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210000901/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2014/Oct-28/275679-lebanon-makes-its-mark-on-bbcs-100-women-list.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

